# everything2md -- environment variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in values as needed.
# See the Installation section of README.md for step-by-step setup instructions.

# Required for Markdown -> PDF (reverse conversion) on Windows.
# WeasyPrint needs GTK/Pango DLLs from MSYS2.
#
# Setup (see README.md Step 7 for full instructions):
#   1. Install MSYS2 from https://www.msys2.org/
#   2. In the MSYS2 MINGW64 shell: pacman -S mingw-w64-x86_64-pango
#   3. Uncomment and set the path below:
#
# WEASYPRINT_DLL_DIRECTORIES=C:\msys64\mingw64\bin
